###Loading data into R  
As a first step we will load data into R using "Load/Chulwalar.R" file.  

```{r }
getwd()
library(knitr)
opts_chunk$set(echo = FALSE, cache=FALSE)
read_chunk('Chulwalar.R')
#read_chunk('Test.R')

```

```{r LoadChulwalarData, echo=FALSE}

```
